      `With ${page.englandFormatted.netMonthly} per month take-home, your housing budget is ${rentBudget30} (30% rule) and maximum mortgage is ${mortgageMax}. These figures provide excellent lifestyle capacity across the entire UK.`,
      `Tax planning is essential in the taper zone. Salary sacrifice pension contributions, charitable giving through Gift Aid, and timing of bonuses can all reduce your adjusted net income. Dropping below £100,000 restores the full ${formatCurrency(PERSONAL_ALLOWANCE)} personal allowance.`,
